  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Fixed: deleting components on a multiple question page</h2>
  <p>You can now delete components from a multiple question page.&nbsp;</p>
  <p>To delete a component:&nbsp;</p>
  <ul>
  <li>click in the component title field to show the component menu (3 dots in a circle)</li>
  <li>click to open the component menu</li>
  <li>select delete and confirm the action&nbsp;</li>
  </ul>
